## Key Design Decisions Made with AI Assistance

| Decision | Rationale |
|----------|-----------|
| Single-file React | Zero setup friction, easy to submit and demo |
| Custom SVG rings | No chart library needed, full control over animation |
| CSS-in-JS style tag | Portable, no build step required |
| Syne + DM Sans fonts | Distinctive, techy, avoids generic AI aesthetics |
| #00E5A0 green accent | High-contrast, wellness/growth association |
| Confetti on completion | Dopamine reward loop for habit formation |
| Synced block toggles | Home + Focus tabs share same state for consistency |
